snippet.title: Genotype - Official Teaser Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Genotype is a VR sci-fi mystery game. Explore an unfamiliar world, adapt to your surroundings, and survive as you try to piece together what happened years ago. Check out this alpha Genotype gameplay for a brief look at the game. Genotype is coming to Meta Quest in late 2023. It's open beta begins on July 17.
